      "value": "Strengthen capacity of 110 district-level government officials, CSOs, Tole Development Committees, child protection duty bearers, children and/or survivors, border patrols, to identify and refer victims of or persons at-risk of transnational TIP in Jhapa and Illam districts.Provide direct assistance to 45 TIP survivors as per individual care plan.Trainings to service providers and caregivers on Mental Health Psychosocial Support and Trauma Informed Care to support rehabilitation of survivors of TIPConduct MPAC meetings in Jhapa and IlamOrganize quarterly review and planning meetingConduct an end-line survey"
